OL,3,CMillions of workers to get new rights
OL,4,Cfrom day one in job under new law
OL,6,FBy ITV News Politics Producer Maya
OL,7,FBowles
OL,9,FMore than seven million people will
OL,10,Fget new employment rights under
OL,11,Flandmark legislation being introduced
OL,12,Fto Parliament.
OL,14,FThe flagship Employment Rights Bill
OL,15,Fwill see immediate access to sick pay
OL,16,Fand parental leave, as well as a ban
OL,17,Fon "exploitative" zero-hour contracts
OL,18,Fand most fire and rehire practices.
