OL,3,CMillions of workers to get new rights
OL,4,Cfrom day one in job under new law
OL,6,FThere will be consultations on a new
OL,7,Fstatutory period, with ministers
OL,8,Fpromising employers a "lighter touch"
OL,9,Fprocess covering dismissals. It's
OL,10,Funderstood the government would like
OL,11,Fthis period to be nine months.
OL,13,FThe Bill also spells out day one
OL,14,Frights for paternity, parental and
OL,15,Fbereavement leave for millions of
OL,16,Fworkers, while statutory sick pay will
OL,17,Fbe paid from the first day of a worker
OL,18,Fbeing sick rather than having to wait
OL,19,Funtil the fourth day.
