OL,3,CMillions of workers to get new rights
OL,4,Cfrom day one in job under new law
OL,6,FAround 30,000 fathers or partners will
OL,7,Fbe eligible for paternity leave, while
OL,8,Fan extra 1.5 million parents will have
OL,9,Fthe right to unpaid leave from day one.
OL,11,FThe Bill doesn't however make any
OL,12,Fchanges to statutory maternity or
OL,13,Fpaternity pay.
OL,15,FFlexible working will be made the
OL,16,Fdefault position "where practical",
OL,17,Fwhile large employers will be required
OL,18,Fto create action plans on addressing
OL,19,Fany gender pay gaps.
