OL,3,CMillions of workers to get new rights
OL,4,Cfrom day one in job under new law
OL,6,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,7,Fsaid the plan "to make work pay is
OL,8,Fcentral to achieving our growth
OL,9,Fmission, boosting productivity".
OL,11,F"After years of stagnation under the
OL,12,FTories, we're replacing a race to the
OL,13,Fbottom with a race to the top, so
OL,14,Femployers compete on innovation and
OL,15,Fquality."
OL,17,FTUC General Secretary Paul Nowak said
OL,18,Fthe Bill "signals a seismic shift away
OL,19,Ffrom the Tories' low pay, low rights,
OL,20,Flow productivity economy", but "there
OL,21,Fis still detail to be worked through."
